## Tech Stack

- **Framework:** Next.js 16 (App Router) with static export (`output: 'export'`)
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS v4 with CSS custom properties for theming
- **Animations:** Framer Motion (component animations) + Lenis (smooth scroll)
- **Form:** React Hook Form + Zod validation
- **Icons:** Lucide React
- **Fonts:** Inter (body) + Space Grotesk (headings) via `next/font`
- **Node version:** 22 (via nvm)

## Architecture

Single-page scrolling website with 9 sections in order:
1. Hero (split-text animation, grid background)
2. About (two-column with circuit SVG)
3. Services (4 glow cards)
4. Stats (count-up counters)
5. Projects (image grid with glow cards)
6. Clients (infinite marquee)
7. FAQ (accordion, drives FAQPage rich snippets)
8. Book Appointment (WhatsApp form via wa.me API)
9. Footer

## Key File Paths

- `app/layout.tsx` — Root layout, fonts, metadata, JSON-LD schemas, theme flash prevention script
- `app/globals.css` — Theme variables (dark default + `[data-theme="light"]`), animations, utilities
- `app/page.tsx` — Composes all sections with SmoothScroll wrapper
- `lib/constants.ts` — ALL company data: phone numbers, services, projects, clients, FAQ, offices
- `lib/whatsapp.ts` — WhatsApp URL builder using `BUSINESS_PHONE` from constants
- `lib/seo.ts` — JSON-LD schema builders (ElectricalContractor, Organization, Service, FAQPage)
- `components/ui/` — Reusable animation primitives (AnimateOnScroll, SplitText, CountUp, GlowCard, Marquee, Button, SectionHeading, ThemeToggle)
- `components/sections/` — All 8 page sections (Hero, About, Services, Stats, Projects, Clients, FAQ, BookAppointment)
- `components/layout/` — Navbar (glass-morphism, mobile menu), Footer, SmoothScroll provider
- `components/seo/StructuredData.tsx` — Reusable JSON-LD script renderer
- `components/icons/Logo.tsx` — SVG logo component
- `public/images/projects/` — Project photos extracted from pitch deck PDF

## Theme System

Colors are defined as CSS custom properties in `:root` (dark) and `[data-theme="light"]`. All Tailwind classes reference these via `@theme inline` bridge. Switching theme only requires changing `data-theme` attribute on `<html>` — no component changes needed.

Key color tokens: `bg-primary`, `bg-surface`, `bg-surface-border`, `accent-cyan`, `accent-amber`, `text-primary`, `text-muted`

## WhatsApp Integration

Form submit builds a pre-filled WhatsApp message and opens `wa.me/{BUSINESS_PHONE}`. The recipient number is `BUSINESS_PHONE` in `lib/constants.ts` (currently `919016150931` — Fenil's number). Format: country code + number, no spaces.

## SEO Strategy

- **Target keywords:** "electrical contractor Gurgaon", "electrical contractor Vadodara", "turnkey electrical solutions", "LT panel manufacturing"
- **Structured data:** ElectricalContractor (LocalBusiness), Organization, Service (x4), FAQPage schemas rendered as JSON-LD in layout.tsx
- **Static files:** `public/sitemap.xml`, `public/robots.txt`, `public/manifest.json`
- **Heading hierarchy:** Single `<h1>` in Hero, all section headings are `<h2>`
- **Semantic HTML:** `<header>`, `<main>`, `<section>` with aria-labels, `<article>`, `<address>`, `<footer>`

