## Conventions

- All client components use `"use client"` directive
- Interactive elements have `min-h-[48px]` for touch targets
- Phone numbers use `tel:` links, email uses `mailto:` link
- Images use `loading="lazy"` and descriptive alt text with keywords
- `prefers-reduced-motion` respected via CSS media query in globals.css
- Mobile-first responsive design using Tailwind breakpoints (sm/md/lg/xl)
